#: 68102c44812f49b69e15b367eee05a63 of
#: tensormesh.assemble.builtin.LaplaceElementAssembler:9
msgid ""
"Given the Laplace equation :math:`-\\nabla \\cdot (\\kappa \\nabla u) = "
"f`, the weak form is:"
